dct_description_sm: Outside cover of brochure published by the New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development of Ringwood Manor State Park. Features a pictoral map indicating streams, museum park office, gardens, trails and other landmarks. Opposite side of page features a table of campsites available and descriptions of the bathing facilities, cabin and boat rentals and hunting grounds. Six photographic illustrations and descriptions of parkland.
